text: Valentina Blažević (born 14 February 1994) is a Croatian handball player for MKS Lublin and the Croatian national team.EHF profile She participated at the 2016 European Women's Handball Championship.2016 European Championship roster ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Croatian female handball players Category:People from Sinj Category:Expatriate handball players in Poland Category:Croatian expatriates in Slovenia Category:Croatian expatriates in Poland
